Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 我来为您更换绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个不中用的家伙 去给我把克洛德叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那双眼睛 我还记忆犹新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火辣辣般地燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来为您更换绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小鬼 要刺的话应该刺更好才对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.21,0:01:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为使用了过大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以导致了轨道的偏离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果用剑的时候再冷静点的话 应该会刺到更深处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更深处？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听你的口吻好像很期待嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不中用 太过于直白而纯粹的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的血的味道如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不渴求我的血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑了 克洛德他…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…难受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:09.49,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}たとえ終わる事の無い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:09.49,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}tatoe owaru koto no nai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:13.26,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}kanashimi ga anata ubattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:13.26,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}悲しみがあなた奪っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:17.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}hanarete yuku kokoro nado
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:17.48,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}離れてゆく心など
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:20.37,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}koko ni wa nai to itte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:20.37,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}此処には無いと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.19,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}kakeyotta senaka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.19,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}駆け寄った背中に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:35.39,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}toikakeru ashita ga donna katachi demo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:35.39,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}問いかける明日がどんあ形でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:38.42,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}yuruga nakatta no wa mou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:38.42,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}揺るがなかったのはもう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:43.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}shinjiru koto wo wasuretaku nakatta kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:43.14,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}信じる事を忘れたくなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:51.55,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}me wo sorasu kuse mo aimai na taido mo waraenu uso mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:51.55,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}目を逸らす癖も 曖昧な回答も 笑えぬ嘘も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:58.82,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}tonari ni inakereba ima sae nijin de yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:58.82,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}隣に居なければ意味さえ 滲んでゆく
